Winter Framework Software Development Kit 1.0.0

This document is the API specification for the Winter Framework modules.

Modules
Module
Description
io.winterframework.core
The Winter Framework core module, providing base elements required by Module classes generated by the Winter Framework compiler.
io.winterframework.core.annotation
The Winter Framework annotation module, providing annotations to be used to create modular applications based on Inversion of Control principle and Dependency Injection.
io.winterframework.mod.base
Defines the foundational APIs of the Winter framework modules.
io.winterframework.mod.boot
The Winter framework boot module provides basic services.
io.winterframework.mod.configuration
The Winter framework configuration module provides advanced application configuration capabilities.
io.winterframework.mod.http.base
The Winter framework HTTP base module defines the base APIs and services for HTTP client and server implementations.
io.winterframework.mod.http.server
The Winter framework HTTP server module provides a HTTP1.x and HTTP/2 server.
io.winterframework.mod.web
The Winter framework Web server module provides a Web enabled HTTP1.x and HTTP/2 server
